# Fact Sheet: Agent Swarms & Orchestration (SYS-AGENTS)

[agents/runtime]
F-001: Orchestration framework must utilize LangGraph to model state transitions. @spec
F-002: Agents run asynchronously, utilizing BullMQ queues to handle LLM delays. @spec @queue
F-003: Chief Editor Agent coordinates work between Research, Fact-Check, and Story swarms. @spec

[agents/safety]
F-004: All LLM payloads must be sanitized and monitored for injection. @spec
F-005: Every agent run must record its duration, cost, and LLM tokens used. @spec @db
